(3321, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep2', '2 Exfil', 'Bob Lee tries to protect his family while incarcerated; and Isaac aims to silence him. In other events, Nadine contacts Bob Lee\'s wife, Julie, who\'s dealing with the backlash against her family.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1szz5gryF8eOTNMFmgqUdOo65jthitkKT/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:43:24', '6936abccee1e5663763', 1),
(3322, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep3', '3 Musa Qala', 'Bob Lee reaches out to Nadine while evading his pursuers; and Isaac juggles his double life while trying to find Bob Lee.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/11SyT3CevlzqBM9SPxK-L0XyeIfT7hkyp/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:43:52', '6936abe8c1db2087335', 1),
(3323, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep4', '4 Overwatch', 'Bob Lee plans his next moves; and Isaac ties up loose ends. In other events, Nadine investigates the Ukrainian connection.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mxOFfksonYKKsJulXG1W3LV81D3IQjse/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:44:23', '6936ac07c810c687526', 1),
(3324, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep5', '5 Recon by Fire', 'Bob Lee locates the bullet from the assassination, which leads him to a radical militia group and Isaac; and Nadine is locked in a deadly game of cat and mouse with Payne.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QD7d-o1UBUIQzAExw40Q-RI1RQgQmNJo/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:44:46', '6936ac1eb40ed547208', 1),
(3325, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep6', '6 Killing Zone', 'Bob Lee tracks down his former instructor, who he hopes will help him find the shooter; Nadine interrogates Payne; Isaac realizes that he\'s in over his head; and a reporter makes Julie an offer.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1lSb7mkQ4F6HvDH6pi5JC7RT35Ises13p/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:45:13', '6936ac39d4349314628', 1),
(3326, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep7', '7 Danger Close', 'Bob Lee travels across the country in order to find the shooter; Julie deals with a family betrayal; Nadine contacts a Ukrainian reporter who can explain the conspiracy; and Isaac questions his allegiance.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WED3tYeSLTJhICGEt_4iEZDlYmWHv0qJ/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:45:41', '6936ac55453b3858546', 1),
(3328, 2043, '6936ab2271e0c515605', 'Shooter Ep8', '8 Red on Red', 'Bob Lee and Nadine plot to secure evidence that could expose the conspiracy. Isaac searches for an exit strategy. Payne tries to flee. Julie and Mary are in danger.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tp1GoKn8p_zTfPzuNKUhDduqlPXWzpSj/preview', '', '2025-12-08 12:52:49', '6936ae012afff504016', 1),
(3329, 2044, '6936ad585b655301746', 'Sean Combs Ep1', '1 Pain vs Love', 'How did a kid from New York transform himself into a powerful hip-hop mogul? The origins of Bad Boy Records reveal how Sean Combs became Puff Daddy.', 'Documentary', '62', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Gop-JHQmCeIqYRalvBNDvft2wEICQA9Q/preview', '', '2025-12-08 13:07:51', '6936b187f2782981975', 8),
