(3337, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep1', '1 The Hunting Party', 'Bob Lee Swagger and wife Julie join his former Marine unit in Germany and narrowly escape a deadly terrorist attack. FBI Agent Nadine Memphis, meanwhile, takes a job in Washington with Patricia Gregson.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1X8md3tGL7jBcuwu3AZo3StMTZbb1l6dI/preview', '', '2025-12-12 21:23:48', '693c6bc4a570d307523', 3),
(3338, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep2', '2 Remember The Alamo', 'Bob Lee investigates the terrorist attack that may have targeted his Marine unit. Memphis helps on the ground in Germany. Flashbacks to Afghanistan help shed light on who might be after them.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Iwc6B1OatJyvW-7JtZKJ4n1zy1b-XNQw/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:51:11', '6945acaf09a89434062', 1),
(3339, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep3', '3 Don\'t Mess With Texas', 'Bob Lee finds Isaac Johnson in Texas after an attempt on his life. Nadine discovers just how much influence Patricia Gregson wields, and a traumatized Julie fights to stay strong for her family.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tuMH_-PoNkr0b2LAxlTR2zcp-4vjRnTK/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:52:18', '6945acf2380cb231460', 1),
(3340, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep4', '4 The Dark End of the Street', 'Bob Lee and Isaac learn the world\'s greatest assassin is in the U.S. Flashbacks to a mission in Afghanistan reveal his identity: Solotov. Nadine comes to Texas with suspicions of a conspiracy.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NQbTndRIYMuDBGvXwHHfpycvZBqF5iXO/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:53:24', '6945ad3480d45840099', 1),
(3341, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep5', '5 The Man Called Noon', 'Bob Lee works to piece together Solotov\'s motive for targeting their unit. Nadine uncovers a surprise witness to the event that set everything off. Solotov\'s hunt has him hiding in plain sight.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l2AomEHDkp7S8F1pD4KzA4j8PQDmroQJ/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:54:42', '6945ad828d330689227', 1),
(3342, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep6', '6 Across the Rio Grande', 'Bob Lee tracks Solotov\'s money, pitting himself against a Mexican cartel. Nadine helps a journalist investigate a cover-up involving Bob Lee\'s unit. Julie makes her frustration heard with a gun.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GXtnYJf1nXr7nLDRxzpNJByyeHhUr0KV/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:55:26', '6945adaeaeba2711293', 1),
(3343, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep7', '7 Someplace Like Bolivia', 'Bob Lee and Isaac must team up to escape a Mexican prison before Solotov finds them. As Nadine digs deeper into Atlas, the cover-up points back to Bob Lee\'s unit. Julie has problems with the law.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UB8uUOrpqhb3Wuo87M86GjrXZo-99sDr/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:56:07', '6945add76743c322133', 1),
(3344, 2045, '693c6b6dab58f727875', 'Shooter S2 Ep8', '8 That\'ll Be the Day [Season Finale]', 'Bob Lee tries to draw out Solotov, but realizes he holds the upper hand; flashbacks reveal the origin of Solotov; Isaac is courted by his creator. Season Finale.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NrBQCqBgaC3qPMUnHSSdQDV2g7mIJVg4/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-19 21:57:09', '6945ae15cbc26567032', 2),
(3345, 2044, '6936ad585b655301746', 'Sean Combs Ep3', '3 Official Girl', 'After Biggie\'s death, Diddy\'s career skyrockets alongside a string of violent incidents. Alarming allegations emerge about abusive relationships.', 'Documentary', '56', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZDcVTWSFkSsK1irzg9vd7tG6KyBKAYPY/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-20 21:38:02', '6946fb1a796a9058120', 1),
(3346, 2046, '694a7800ccb77657092', 'Shooter S3 Ep1', '1 Backroads', 'ulie and Isaac team up to save Bob Lee after he is kidnapped by Solotov; Nadine confronts Hayes about Atlas; new information about Bob Lee\'s father, Earl Swagger, sets off a new mission.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OQrZuSd34P55aFJUrJpKc3hsaHYXvTL1/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 13:09:39', '694a787316538800396', 3),
(3347, 2046, '694a7800ccb77657092', 'Shooter S3 Ep2', '2 Red Meat', 'Bob Lee visits a local prison for answers about his father\'s murder; Julie takes a job helping the family lawyer; Nadine and Isaac grab Harris Downey, who knows more about Atlas than he realizes.', 'Action', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1s22xyd8BmCVLDukw8TwfUAFnWeUOy3aB/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 13:10:16', '694a78985e5f0251839', 1),
(3348, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep1', '1 Deuk Pal Goes to High School', 'Deuk Pal is about to become the boss of the Chilsung Gang. While mulling over giving up his dream of going to university, he tries to save Yi Heon from jumping off a bridge. Unfortunately, Deuk Pal loses his life but takes over Yi Heon\'s body. He learns of Yi Heon\'s misfortunes and resolves to avenge his suffering as a victim of bullying.', 'Drama', '53', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mjIKHyfBdF41ubBK7wP16ROin1nVpHWE/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:52:24', '694a90888a426523376', 5),
(3349, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep2', '2 You Are Not Song Yi Heon', 'Deuk Pal, now inhabiting Yi Heonâ€™s body, arouses suspicion from Se Kyung due to his noticeable deviation from his usual self. Despite Deuk Pal\'s attempts to mimic Yi Heon\'s behaviour, the other kids begin to question the sudden change in him. Particularly with Jae Min persisting in ridiculing Yi Heon, Deuk Pal plots a subtle revenge for him.', 'Drama', '54', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wABnmhnW21vOVDrRAZeo-8Vk6LP0YJLF/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:53:05', '694a90b193c27561046', 2),
(3350, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep3', '3 Deuk Pal Takes Charge', 'Deuk Pal proves he can fight in Yi Heon\'s body and gains control over Jae Min and his underlings. The kids at school can\'t believe how different Yi Heon is and are shocked. Se Kyung gets DNA testing done to see if Yi Heon is still the Yi Heon he knows, and Deuk Pal focuses on his studies and setting things right for Yi Heon. Meanwhile, Deuk Pal learns about what happened the night before Yi Heon died from Se Kyung as they become closer.', 'Drama', '54', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yeIa-xkdB045u_jIl5C6AbeM3gcuntnB/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:53:50', '694a90de4b744230614', 2),
(3351, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep4', '4 Yi Heon\'s Mom Kidnapping', 'Deuk Pal and Se Kyung save Yi Heon\'s mom from getting kidnapped. Luckily, she was unharmed. Although he has a hunch about who might be responsible, Deuk Pal vows to protect Yi Heon and his family without the police involved. Meanwhile, Jae Min approaches Deuk Pal to find out if the police are looking for him, but Se Kyung confronts him about his involvement in the attempted kidnapping.', 'Drama', '51', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bryWGP-k5x1twvHZZyfPtcNUCjgip9s4/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:54:26', '694a9102b3ab4256379', 1),
(3352, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep5', '5 Yi Heon Warns Dong Soo', 'Se Kyung witnesses Yi Heon getting abducted but can\'t do anything about it because he remembers Yi Heon telling him not to call the police about anything. He asks Jae Min for help, but Jae Min cowards out. Meanwhile, Yi Heon deals with the gangsters and tells them things that shock them.', 'Drama', '52', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1LJe7o1R9wdpU8jmPOrbL_F0c6FGbrptW/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:55:19', '694a9137d8c27212417', 1),
(3353, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep6', '6 Reach Out', 'Deuk Pal and Se Kyung go to see the ocean and have a day off. Se Kyung talks about his father whoâ€™s been trying to control him since young and how it made him stressed and suffocating. Se Kyungâ€™s father comes to school and calls for the violence committee. Meanwhile, Deuk Pal finds out that Yi Heonâ€™s mother has been taking addictive medicine.', 'Drama', '56', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1D59Zb3Sy6RCFhCxJOf4iY7WgpzlI_6LB/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:55:53', '694a9159a49a2674895', 1),
(3354, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep7', '7 This Is Your Last Chance', 'Deuk Pal found out that the school bullies reported Yi Heon for school violence. He orders Dong Soo and the gang to get Lee Mi Kyung since she is the one behind them. Byung Chul tells Jae Min to join him and report Yi Heon as well. Jae Min feels guilty about falsely charging Yi Heon, but he\'s also scared that he might end up going to the juvie if the truth is revealed.', 'Drama', '53', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MI_vXcNhh6TLhXsWnKnwvhurX0u8MKgn/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:56:26', '694a917a7d845611393', 1),
(3355, 2047, '694a90477b315969671', 'High School Ep8', '8 Goodbye [Season Finale]', 'Jae Min confesses to bullying Yi Heon and other kids at school. Thanks to Jae Min, the charges are dropped, but Deuk Pal still needs to find Mi Kyung so that she won\'t come back to threaten Yi Heon and his mother again. He decides to meet Chairman Bae and set everything right. Meanwhile, Yi Heon\'s soul returns and tells Deuk Pal that he does not have much time left.', 'Drama', '66', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MyMIF2APejRytpKPfhAFgG8cKASA76K-/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-23 14:57:13', '694a91a9b71ca342614', 1),
(3356, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep1', '1 The Year I Lived Two Lives', 'Miranda watches ClÃ©o entertain a customer. When ClÃ©o decides to go away for the weekend, Miranda agrees to take care of her little dog.', 'Drama', '51', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qzrJ4nL3RuRvE-9g2n7uHA2vmp0c1R1O/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:27:15', '695122233f7c1265637', 1),
(3357, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep2', '2 Every Action Has a Reaction', 'Cleo turns to Miranda for help, but a bunch of different problems start popping up. Diana tells Fernando the truth about LuÃ­sa.', 'Drama', '39', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TipXKyXaLGbPylfEFZ1XxPpSF8TWoiC8/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:28:24', '695122685c6e8339925', 0),
(3358, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep3', '3 Fragmented', 'Miranda manages to get away, but her memories of what happened the night before are pretty vague. Detective InÃªs investigates what happened to Diana.', 'Drama', '39', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1498W9uDa5JWS3RY0BOdZ2jx0VEpBGzja/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:41:58', '695125962628e739806', 0),
(3359, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep4', '4 The Perfect Lie', 'Miranda discovers a secret about Diana\'s past. Zoe\'s behavior puts her in the sights of Detective InÃªs and Miranda.', 'Drama', '46', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ne2t_OJe7FslJvk4hG_vOwOYBUOOiu4x/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:42:48', '695125c806d99607187', 0),
(3360, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep5', '5 Crime and Punishment', 'Detective InÃªs investigates Helena. Miranda begins to suspect that Heitor is involved in Cleo\'s disappearance. Zoe resorts to blackmail.', 'Drama', '46', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1_I0pDa0gy7gk2Ga95T9OvxdX_iHxD5uf/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:43:44', '695126008105d535612', 1),
(3361, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep6', '6 Shadows of the Past', 'After being questioned by Detective InÃªs, Miranda helps LuÃ­sa. Authorities identify a new suspect in Diana\'s case.', 'Drama', '41', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cIdl2_JZZRcNzfN0r1yZdlr5aAjjo0KE/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:44:41', '69512639b25e9504372', 0),
(3362, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep7', '7 She\'s Among Us', 'Rafael fights with Heitor and Miranda is worried about Rita, who could be in danger. VitÃ³ria shocks the family with an unexpected revelation.', 'Drama', '41', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZpuMq2-Chpne-968D55kVIL7j1GK7wgV/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:45:31', '6951266b9d216641114', 0),
(3363, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep8', '8 Rock Bottom Is the Hottest Place', 'Detective InÃªs interrogates ClÃ©o. Miranda suspects that Fernando is up to something. A new inspector joins the investigation.', 'Drama', '41', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1K3LBfnEP3HpJ1Q2xSGv22e6Jc-8uFy3u/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:46:39', '695126af42aec827405', 0),
(3364, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep9', '9 Going, Going... Gone!', 'After opening up to Detective InÃªs, Miranda does everything to discover the truth about Heitor. LuÃ­sa and VinÃ­cius run away together.', 'Drama', '39', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zt14jG_9z06F5o_5ir47AZYSHR0dPCtc/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:48:31', '6951271fbb54c381446', 0),
(3365, 2048, '695121a018df8703579', 'Lady Voyeur Ep10', '10 The Past Is Outside, The Future Is in Here', 'Shaken by Cleo\'s confession, Miranda wonders who she really is. The family begins to unravel under the weight of all the secrets from the past.', 'Drama', '56', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Np6zDAWl_XfFuIQ0COX3fMAYxqAN9F4Q/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:49:29', '695127598da91112862', 2),
(3366, 2049, '695128035a9c1680564', 'Nine Bodies in a Mexican Morgue Ep1', '1 Dead Reckoning', 'Nine people survive a plane crash into the Mexican jungle. But they donâ€™t know that a murderer lurks in their midstâ€¦ Nine days later, their bodies are recovered by the Mexican army. One of the passengers is missing...but who?', 'Drama', '64', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AagmQhxBxakIKe9dB3R63Mq5-19f8Ul2/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:54:19', '6951287bcc128084737', 3),
(3367, 2049, '695128035a9c1680564', 'Nine Bodies in a Mexican Morgue Ep2', '2 Black Angels', 'Alliances form, enemies are made and lines are drawn as the passengers search for food and water; but when another passenger dies, they realize they may all be targets.', 'Drama', '60', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pNCNtG7xF-B4YrOsog0T4zLu4NSYoMQM/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:55:04', '695128a8eb6c5677628', 3),
(3368, 2049, '695128035a9c1680564', 'Nine Bodies in a Mexican Morgue Ep3', '3 Rapido', 'The survivors work out how to call for help - but are faced with a treacherous climb; as some of the group begin to crack under the pressure, a third death - the most violent so far - warns that they are running out of time.', 'Drama', '61', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HpB-tLHu8tdTti4zpFwpb1cHjkYB0fF0/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:55:50', '695128d623da2223783', 6),
(3369, 2049, '695128035a9c1680564', 'Nine Bodies in a Mexican Morgue Ep4', '4 The Short Straw', 'The deadly secret hidden in Flight CBZ517 is discovered, but it still doesn\'t explain the murders or help the survivors escape; the passengers believe they have found the traitor in the group - but are they right?', 'Drama', '62', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1H_ktRjaXM43MmR65j34hji90OrX1yUDM/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:56:32', '6951290089c7d663084', 2),
(3370, 2049, '695128035a9c1680564', 'Nine Bodies in a Mexican Morgue Ep5', '5 Cloud Cover', 'Air authorities search desperately for the plane and federal agencies spring into action; as the group becomes smaller and smaller, the last survivors know they are going to have to fight to stay alive.', 'Drama', '67', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/14YeKz1UiqrsF2u-wTGD420gzi9J85a_H/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2025-12-28 14:57:41', '6951294539877462489', 5),
