(3425, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep3', '3 Clean Skin', 'Brody prepares to enter the spotlight; Carrie closes in on an al-Qaeda plot.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1eN9D6kMp-JCp7HU2RkaWfbJaEiXG483E/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:06:56', '695df80025eff698810', 5),
(3426, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep4', '4 Semper I', 'The political powers that be make big plans for national hero Brody, but his increasingly erratic behavior threatens his media darling status; Carrie grows desperate for evidence linking Brody with Abu Nazir, as Saul directs her to focus on Nazir\'s money trail.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/19TwCllvcmi8YqBj1RR0cMapscW8pR1c9/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:07:28', '695df8204eac6206768', 3),
(3427, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep5', '5 Blind Spot', 'Brody confronts the lone survivor among the insurgents that held him, leading Carrie to believe she may be proved right about Brody once and for all - but Brody\'s reunion with his captor surprises everyone; the agency is hot on the trail of the lovers who bought a house near the airport with funds from a stolen necklace.', 'Drama', '56', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/121oIUq-vabcIlryZfLTA4vH3gviD_f91/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:07:58', '695df83e989cc849080', 3),
(3428, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep6', '6 The Good Soldier', 'Reeling after losing key players in Nazir\'s plot against America, the CIA orders polygraphs on everyone who came in contact with them, including Brody, which Carrie sees as an opportunity to finally learn the truth.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ahgh9u6TnVhoRy0P0QnAV21QY66JpkGN/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:08:31', '695df85f4198f973089', 3),
(3429, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep7', '7 The Weekend', 'The relationship between Carrie and Brody becomes more complicated when they head into the countryside for the weekend, while Mike and Jessica face the fallout of the truth about their relationship, and Saul catches Aileen on the run to Mexico.', 'Drama', '59', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1H5VBnSyjL9JAKw99l2vf2MHdZg5ctLmh/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:09:02', '695df87e48fc6686406', 2),
(3430, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep1', '1 The Energy of Love', 'During his glory days, Berlin assembles a gang in Paris for an almost impossible heist for 44 million euros\' worth of jewels from 34 cities in one night.', 'Drama', '58', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oYNJBoDVKWXG1wSZhxLOzHsKXmZC6QHb/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:14:16', '695df9b8632cb364572', 12),
(3431, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep2', '2 Anchor and Lobo', 'Roi and Cameron must stop Father Toureaux as he threatens to bungle the plan. Meanwhile, love is in the air on Paris\'s streets â€” and in the Catacombs.', 'Drama', '51', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/17B5Yajk_j9n9aJklGCwrLpL6I5rbWj1z/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:14:52', '695df9dc9307d279651', 5),
(3432, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep3', '3 Full House of Embryos', 'Everything seems to be rolling along â€” for a short while. While Berlin schemes to get his way with both the heist and Camille, DamiÃ¡n gets some bad news.', 'Drama', '44', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1i8Lb13J_VI-Ij6MEhhI7ASweE0a4ZW1e/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:15:22', '695df9fa6d852207123', 7),
(3433, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep4', '4 An Aquarium on Your Back', 'The robbery is on and tensions are high as the crew starts to doubt Berlin\'s leadership. Keila and Bruce must make sure to cover their tracks.', 'Drama', '43', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1CiGY6WbSme48H9pvLWxufyFfChbWNpjW/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:16:10', '695dfa2add97a176934', 6),
(3434, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep5', '5 After Love', 'Cameron\'s resurfaced trauma bursts in at an illegal street race. The plan enters a new phase as the gang flees the police, who are hot on their heels.', 'Drama', '47', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1T9Y4BtWmxk8rAolGsOG9mEDbv8v30Azn/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:17:01', '695dfa5d753d3545005', 2),
(3435, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep6', '6 Night of the Lemons', 'Camille\'s suspicions heighten. DamiÃ¡n, Cameron and Roi have a troubling encounter, shaking the entire gang\'s alibis. A loose end emerges in Paris.', 'Drama', '42', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OSdCn8x-233q3Igq7Dc3zHuzb6fgW0ni/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:17:41', '695dfa85eaf6f974994', 0),
(3436, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep7', '7 The Last Virgin in the Western World', 'As Bruce helps Keila with a life-or-death situation, Sierra and Murillo join the French police to look into the theft. Berlin suffers an ultimate defeat.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1giJA55J555o1EzDBlbtUJEh_Y0qJ5L_s/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:18:17', '695dfaa9bf2b3994324', 0),
(3437, 2057, '695df9781b828877017', 'Berlin Ep8', '8 An Endangered Elephant [Season Finale]', 'Backed into a corner, the gang maneuvers a final escape plan. Only time will tell if Berlin is ready for the ultimate bombshell.', 'Drama', '61', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yBW4ReNudDdNY2VgoBmuiwBVm4Ztxasi/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:19:09', '695dfadd5afa2486909', 3),
(3438, 2058, '695dfd127c2b5455208', 'Money Heist: Korea Ep1', '1 Episode 1', 'Recruited by the Professor for a job of unprecedented proportions, eight thieves storm the Unified Korea Mint. Police pull together a task force.', 'Action', '79', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gFB6GCqvKnRDU4Ftlz5IkaPQcDQeLzQS/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:29:52', '695dfd609d2df424046', 14),
(3439, 2058, '695dfd127c2b5455208', 'Money Heist: Korea Ep2', '2 Episode 2', 'Seon Woojin waits for a crack in the thieves\' operation. An escape plan centered around the retrieval of a hidden smartwatch puts Yun Misun in danger.', 'Action', '75', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1LLqYX35qukHateCw6zN2skU52q3DwVdp/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:30:25', '695dfd81c6ae8702934', 7),
(3440, 2058, '695dfd127c2b5455208', 'Money Heist: Korea Ep3', '3 Episode 3', 'The sound of a gunshot shakes up the Mint. Dissent among the thieves reaches new heights as some believe a line has been crossed.', 'Action', '69', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1a0A1ZwbJe_-h_kMwiVL0VX5A3bhVmYBj/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:30:55', '695dfd9fcbc6d615275', 7),
(3441, 2058, '695dfd127c2b5455208', 'Money Heist: Korea Ep4', '4 Episode 4', 'Looking to turn a potential disaster into an opportunity, Woojin presses the Professor to allow medical personnel to enter the Mint.', 'Action', '71', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Wj-zEKRHLyFFzUQamZ-wVC1w9_lvryFo/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:31:28', '695dfdc0d02c2971859', 7),
(3442, 2058, '695dfd127c2b5455208', 'Money Heist: Korea Ep5', '5 Episode 5', 'Cha Moohyuk hurries a plot of his own into action. A key revelation on Woojin\'s end threatens to unravel the Professor\'s strategy.', 'Action', '65', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/115Go991AVMMW8wxdKkxYaiZuRuuAS0ng/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:32:07', '695dfde7a4440877990', 6),
(3443, 2058, '695dfd127c2b5455208', 'Money Heist: Korea Ep6', '6 Episode 6 - [Mid-Season Finale]', 'As those outside the Mint panic, Woojin proposes she go inside with a cameraman so the thieves can show the public that the hostages are unharmed.', 'Action', '64', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ftnJOvNENoMhhZCHrmB2FsUBBZBWJSQh/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 08:32:59', '695dfe1b154ab339031', 7),
(3444, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep8', '8 Achilles Heel', 'As Carrie and Saul reel from the news that Walker is alive, the intelligence community clashes on the best way to capture him; Brody learns a shocking truth about his captivity.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UH77YSVSr641DURHKtyh8NLvhTOITPTN/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 22:46:58', '695ec642c288d040302', 2),
(3445, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep9', '9 Crossfire', 'After his attempt to sever ties with Abu Nazir, Brody finds himself reliving his captivity and recommits to his mission; Carrie finds herself in the middle of a public relations nightmare on the heels of the mosque shooting.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uTi3FYwWaGduy64M3ky3ZwXn3_OMEt_k/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 22:47:33', '695ec665c354b089071', 2),
(3446, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep10', '10 Representative Brody', 'Carrie and Saul identify Walker\'s contact in Washington but their target has diplomatic immunity; Brody is approached to run for a disgraced congressman\'s seat in the House of Representatives.', 'Drama', '49', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1JJLd2CpjuB4pDuRPwwsnHaeOJ2XzTguE/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-07 22:48:09', '695ec689dede4660870', 2),
(3447, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep11', '11 The Vest', 'In the wake of the explosion, Saul finds Carrie hospitalized and manic, but realizes her chaotic theories have merit; before his congressional campaign begins, Brody takes his family on a weekend trip to Gettysburg, where he retrieves an important item.', 'Drama', '55', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PI_KFnwL5epZOd2_Jcepa-3lKELBu1CR/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-08 11:38:11', '695f7b037463e792312', 3),
(3448, 2052, '6959515c17cbb240152', 'Homeland S1 Ep12', '12 Marine One  [Season Finale]', 'While Carrie is near catatonic and confined to bed, Saul investigates the unsettling implications of her timeline; Walker secures a perch for his mission; Brody makes his final preparations for the Vice President\'s policy summit at the State Department.', 'Drama', '85', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1doTtGZSlKCvYNgm2XZp_-Sc1WWrfG6VX/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-08 11:39:43', '695f7b5f19f48788108', 5),
(3449, 2059, '696479f248eb6725082', 'Homeland S2 Ep1', '1 The Smile', 'Brody has been elected to Congress. A woman named Roya comes to see him, and asks him to steal a list of homeland targets from Estes\'s office safe. Carrie is working with the CIA again because Fatima, an informant married to a man working for Abu Nazir, tells Saul that she\'ll only speak to Carrie. Estes goes to pick up Carrie at her sister\'s house, and then she\'s sent to Cyprus, where she\'s prepped for a brief mission in Lebanon.', 'Drama', '56', '', '', '2026-01-12 06:37:20', '69647a805b6a2434540', 6),
(3450, 2059, '696479f248eb6725082', 'Homeland S2 Ep2', '2 Beirut is Back', 'Fatima tells Carrie about a meeting her husband - a Hezbollah commander - will be having in Beirut with Abu Nazir, and Carrie and Saul call Estes to tell him and to request a special forces team to capture Nazir.', 'Drama', '46', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1d_6X6jnQBbv-8CQnUJ1l9KL3wHImZNDF/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-12 06:38:15', '69647ab70452f710044', 7),
(3451, 2059, '696479f248eb6725082', 'Homeland S2 Ep3', '3 State of Independence', 'Colonel Lubaid, who briefly detains Saul at the Rafic Hariri airport in Beirut as Saul is leaving Lebanon', 'Drama', '55', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1G7pTYebh0a3vIVRGVSNonqPOMQXwXMoW/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-12 06:38:52', '69647adc1dd63609452', 3),
(3452, 2059, '696479f248eb6725082', 'Homeland S2 Ep4', '4 New Car Smell', 'Brody takes his car to be professionally cleaned and to have a strong smoke smell removed. Max and Virgil follow Brody and take photos of him. Brody then takes a cab to CIA Headquarters, where Carrie waits inside for his arrival. As he walks towards the building from the parking lot, she exits and walks past him. He is very surprised to see her and calls her name. She turns and greets him casually.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/120lQRPEUKgLW77SNN8w8pCQGFw1yWgm6/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-12 06:39:29', '69647b018c9b8836863', 3),
(3453, 2059, '696479f248eb6725082', 'Homeland S2 Ep5', '5 Q&A', 'Brody finds himself prisoner again, but this time it\'s on American soil. Meanwhile, Carrie is forced to play second fiddle after her rash judgment call at the hotel as Estes is busy keeping Jessica off their trail. Dana\'s relationship with Finn goes to the next level when their date night turns deadly serious.', 'Drama', '57', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Obq-lKOixDVE6Fo2-ugGt8XvP7mkh6wD/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-12 06:40:10', '69647b2af0426377391', 3),
(3454, 2059, '696479f248eb6725082', 'Homeland S2 Ep6', '6 A Gettysburg Address', 'Dana is shocked by her visit to the hospital. Faber\'s Tom Walker questions get him tangled up with the CIA. Brody agrees to help stop an attack on America, but his loyalty is questioned when Gettysburg once again becomes a battleground.', 'Drama', '50', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zRJrnhDQuEDaakNquHcDY3kVeXXIocuz/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-12 06:40:55', '69647b578a723724316', 3),
(3455, 2060, '6968961cca594038679', 'Hwarang Ep1', '1 To the Capital', 'In Silla about 1,500 years ago, Queen Jiso reluctantly receives an unexpected visitor and two friends go to the capital in search of family.', 'Drama', '60', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1b4HYxJTtFHDF3sE8Nufol1yYahggbh8t/view?usp=drive_link', '', '2026-01-15 09:26:06', '6968968e57ade995930', 12);
