(1094, 'Until Dawn', 'One year after her sister Melanie mysteriously disappeared, Clover and her friends head into the remote valley where she vanished in search of answers. Exploring an abandoned visitor center, they find themselves stalked by a masked killer and horrifically murdered one by one...only to wake up and find themselves back at the beginning of the same evening.', 'Horror', 2025, '118', 'Gaheza', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XTf8oGWru_lnvH37AWffOA1KJo0NTxrA/preview', '', '1762582413.webp', 'No', 'sdZtJvOJts', '2025-11-08 08:13:32', '690edf8c8efac202270', '6.4', 2, NULL),
(1095, 'Operation Dumbo Drop', 'Five Green Berets stationed in Vietnam in 1968 grudgingly undertake the mission of a lifetime -- to secretly transport an 8,000-pound elephant through 200 miles of rough jungle terrain. High jinks prevail when Capt. Sam Cahill promises the Montagnard villagers of Dak Nhe that he\'ll replace their prized elephant in time for an important ritual. But for Capt. T.C. Doyle, the mission becomes a jumbo-sized headache!', 'Action', 1995, '71', 'Rocky', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/14iCEsi8GM2Jhz879rYsGEM01yOUnyIsW/preview', '', '1762707211.webp', 'No', 'vdqvJso99I', '2025-11-09 18:53:31', '6910c70b4cfee307250', '5.2', 2, NULL),
(1096, 'Heads of State A', 'The UK Prime Minister and US President have a public rivalry that risks their countries\' alliance. But when they become targets of a powerful enemy, they\'re forced to rely on each other as they go on a wild, multinational run. Allied with Noel, a brilliant MI6 agent, they must find a way to thwart a conspiracy that threatens the free world.', 'Action', 2025, '69', 'Rocky', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BZsPzfbN53KI4f2fL77hHf8_M0eE3GtA/preview', '', '1762707659.webp', 'No', '5nKyf45JIZ', '2025-11-09 19:00:58', '6910c8caca602435223', '6.9', 2, NULL),
