(1310, 'We Bury the Dead', '<b>| 01/02/2026 (US) - Horror and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nAfter a catastrophic military disaster, the dead don\'t just riseâ€”they hunt. The military insists they are harmless and slow-moving, offering hope to grieving families. But when Ava enters a quarantine zone searching for her missing husband, she uncovers the horrifying truth: the undead are growing more violent, more relentless, and more dangerous with every passing hour.', 'Horror', 2026, '96', 'Perfect', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/ba90sni4zuzw', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QVLaUO65bSJYEsjtdXl4dQyI3MhxGwJ9/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/we-bury-the-dead-7664.jpg', 'No', 'yKYqJhS9co', '2026-02-22 05:55:05', '699a7e19a6eac960610', '6.3', 6, NULL),
(1311, 'Misdirection', '<b>| 02/10/2026 (US) - Horror and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nA desperate couple have pulled off a string of high-end break-ins to pay off a mob debt. When they attempt to rob their latest victim, they find themselves caught in a deadly game of cat and mouse. The tables are turned and the hunters become the hunted.', 'Horror', 2026, '93', 'Rumuri', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/5yom2a3b75oy', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uqNzG2-QkeabgT9ikfoL5vbppZEzQubk/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/misdirection-8108.jpg', 'No', 'PgASoSPBPL', '2026-02-22 12:55:15', '699ae0934b6ba780438', '5.8', 3, NULL),
