(1369, 'Night Teeth', '<b>| 10/20/2021 (GB) Horror, Thriller, and Action.</b><br>\r\nA college student moonlighting as a chauffeur picks up two mysterious women for a night of party-hopping across LA. But when he uncovers their bloodthirsty intentionsâ€”and their dangerous, shadowy underworldâ€”he must fight to stay alive.', 'Horror', 2021, '111', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/v5vzg9pupe9n', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GLXDrrPRIzs4PcVvZJLvO3eUdWWHQMxb/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/night-teeth-2572.jpg', 'No', 'icUCFrnO17', '2026-03-12 11:00:08', '69b2809846cb6958797', '6.4', 19, NULL),
(1370, 'Back to the Past', '<b>|  12/31/2025 (CN) Science Fiction, Action, and Comedy.</b><br>\r\nIn the Qin Dynasty, time-traveller Hong Siu-lung has lived in seclusion with his family for twenty years. Yet every step he takes remains under the watchful eye of his former disciple, now the Qin Emperor. On the brink of ultimate power after conquering the six warring states, the emperor is suddenly ambushed by a mysterious team wielding advanced weapons clearly originating from Hongâ€™s time. Drawn together by fate again, Hong and Qin Emperor are forced to confront the long-buried conflict between them, because the future now depends on how they settle their past.', 'Sci-Fi', 2025, '98', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/00fpqnpn2c7g', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/16WhC0oO7OMkqmnahiWviH5-gaZh21jfh/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/back-to-the-past-1135.jpg', 'No', 'hmSSjzNRO7', '2026-03-15 16:57:19', '69b6c8cf8a2b6227904', '6', 5, NULL),
(1371, 'Friend Request', '<b>| 01/02/2020 (US) Thriller.</b><br>\r\nThe reappearance of an old flame puts a district attorney\'s career in jeopardy.', 'Drama', 2019, '91', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/0lx7erey7xmc', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MwIS4PcvFh3_1v6wNW5KhcwSunfhSsyY/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/friend-request-8241.jpg', 'No', 'EDyrgpIfGZ', '2026-03-15 20:14:14', '69b6f6f6c033d059910', '7.3', 15, NULL),
(1372, 'The Cure', '<b>| 05/15/2020 (US) Action.</b><br>\r\nIn the near future, a mysterious virus has taken over a large portion of the world\'s population.Upon contamination, it kills the host within a day. There is no permanent cure, only a temporary serum that resets every 24 hours.Special forces mercenary Noah\'s young daughter is one of the infected. When a permanent cure is stolen from a top-secret lab by a mysterious terrorist organization,Noah is recruited to retrieve it and ultimately save his daughter\'s life.What starts as an already dangerous mission turns into a deathtrap when the terrorists\' bring fifteen armored vehicles filled with a hundred trained killer armed to the teeth with assault rifles, grenades, and even a rocket launcher. On top of this, the covert government organization that hired Noah might also have ulterior motives for the cure. Now Noah has to race against time to protect the one thing that can save his daughter\'s life as the chase turns into a symphony of ultraviolent action; filled with vehicular carnage,...', 'Action', 2020, '48', 'Sankara', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/032p5g4dbhkx', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GVLvEDCoH7eezEyhx70dRrcx0t1m5y4F/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-cure-1450.jpg', 'No', 'PCuzDgRye7', '2026-03-15 20:18:36', '69b6f7fc55475301941', '7.3', 17, NULL),
(1373, 'The Cure 2', '<b>| 05/15/2020 (US) Action .</b><br>\r\nIn the near future, a mysterious virus has taken over a large portion of the world\'s population.Upon contamination, it kills the host within a day. There is no permanent cure, only a temporary serum that resets every 24 hours.Special forces mercenary Noah\'s young daughter is one of the infected. When a permanent cure is stolen from a top-secret lab by a mysterious terrorist organization,Noah is recruited to retrieve it and ultimately save his daughter\'s life.What starts as an already dangerous mission turns into a deathtrap when the terrorists\' bring fifteen armored vehicles filled with a hundred trained killer armed to the teeth with assault rifles, grenades, and even a rocket launcher. On top of this, the covert government organization that hired Noah might also have ulterior motives for the cure. Now Noah has to race against time to protect the one thing that can save his daughter\'s life as the chase turns into a symphony of ultraviolent action; filled with vehicular carnage,...', 'Action', 2020, '12', 'Sankara', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/bzbm7h01f81y', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MyEGo-IXyi8-3tjyUU1AtODD7wvQNcbX/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-cure-2-9147.jpg', 'Yes', 'PCuzDgRye7', '2026-03-15 20:27:46', '69b6fa22e790e444432', '7.3', 4, NULL),
(1374, 'Carry-On', '<b>| 12/13/2024 (RW) Thriller and Action.</b><br>\r\nAn airport security officer races to outsmart a mysterious traveler forcing him to let a dangerous item slip onto a Christmas Eve flight.', 'Action', 2024, '108', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/p01swi0ycnoq', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Uaf5pG7FfA_wdjIkPxLIV8urFEo-6pZ-/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/carry-on-9538.jpg', 'No', 'thOenqeXal', '2026-03-16 08:04:21', '69b79d654e7e0398317', '6.9', 15, NULL),
(1375, 'The Bluff B', '<b>| 02/17/2026 (US) Action and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nWhen her tranquil life on a remote island is shattered by the return of her vengeful former captain, a skilled ex-pirate must confront her bloody past and unleash her deadly talents to save her family from a ruthless siege.', 'Action', 2026, '44', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/3gfq3dpm6eph', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gfcTC0-Hfip1cd0vOLi1YXqJVzuPUz5C/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-bluff-b-5992.jpg', 'No', '7FudhJFNK4', '2026-03-18 22:42:53', '69bb0e4d4a48a084549', '6.3', 15, NULL),
(1376, 'Kill \'em All', '<b>| 04/01/2013 (US) Action, Crime, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nCaptured international assassins are locked up inside a high-tech bunker known as the Killing Chamber. To break out of this concrete hell they must duel each other, fight deadly ninjas and battle against gangs of masked maniacs. And... if they survive this, they will have to confront Snakehead: the lethal, deranged top dog who will stop at nothing to kill \'em all!', 'Action', 2012, '86', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/0696fsht14xo', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1s60wNACr-T3RLEwkCUKX67e6KqrTRbio/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/kill-em-all-8128.jpg', 'No', 'kNV3TEd0fW', '2026-03-19 18:03:48', '69bc1e64ebc43438737', '5.2', 5, NULL),
(1377, 'Scream VI', '<b>| 03/10/2023 (US) Horror, Thriller, and Crime.</b><br>\r\nFollowing the latest Ghostface killings, the four survivors leave Woodsboro behind and start a fresh chapter.', 'Horror', 2023, '127', 'Sankara', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/kouocv3985i0', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dYPan_HMY9QVyc-jal51Zsmev1TJev4c/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/scream-vi-9192.jpg', 'No', 'qrCGmoZZvw', '2026-03-19 19:11:35', '69bc2e4729798716674', '7', 7, NULL),
(1378, 'The Equalizer', '<b>| 09/26/2014 (US) Thriller, Action, and Crime.</b><br>\r\nMcCall believes he has put his mysterious past behind him and dedicated himself to beginning a new, quiet life. But when he meets Teri, a young girl under the control of ultra-violent Russian gangsters, he canâ€™t stand idly by â€“ he has to help her. Armed with hidden skills that allow him to serve vengeance against anyone who would brutalize the helpless, McCall comes out of his self-imposed retirement and finds his desire for justice reawakened. If someone has a problem, if the odds are stacked against them, if they have nowhere else to turn, McCall will help. He is The Equalizer.', 'Action', 2014, '133', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/g0vfejch9y68', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hzXYjYMH4CXiRh7ecOYMasQoTxHFr26-/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-equalizer-6137.jpg', 'No', 'Of8ffDlUQq', '2026-03-19 20:51:18', '69bc45a636a52696207', '7.3', 7, NULL),
(1379, 'The Equalizer 2', '<b>| 07/20/2018 (US) Action, Thriller, and Crime.</b><br>\r\nRobert McCall, who serves an unflinching justice for the exploited and oppressed, embarks on a relentless, globe-trotting quest for vengeance when his former partner is murdered.', 'Action', 2018, '121', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/ydhy05kx09gp', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BTA0DuRh5f0Il_wal9oVyvPDCAvjt3Kk/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-equalizer-2-4884.jpg', 'No', 'Of8ffDlUQq', '2026-03-19 20:54:14', '69bc4656efad7044497', '6.8', 6, NULL),
(1380, 'Fast x', '<b>| 05/19/2023 (US) Action, Crime, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nOver many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they\'ve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who\'s fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everythingâ€”and everyoneâ€”that Dom loves, forever.', 'Action', 2023, '132', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/aq1mvl1fyqx6', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TnwIuxRjYpfnmORchl6i1g9-BR6WHa_l/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/fast-x-4019.jpg', 'No', 'vQ05VUk9YH', '2026-03-19 21:07:36', '69bc49785ec88903509', '7', 7, NULL),
(1381, 'The Equalizer 3', '<b>| 09/01/2023 (US) Action, Thriller, and Crime.</b><br>\r\nRobert McCall finds himself at home in Southern Italy but he discovers his friends are under the control of local crime bosses. As events turn deadly, McCall knows what he has to do: become his friends\' protector by taking on the mafia.', 'Action', 2023, '110', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/p61dajlxk3gp', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l5lbhoQRxhvzG2jFwu63pAgIbD1E4fii/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-equalizer-3-1210.jpg', 'No', 'Of8ffDlUQq', '2026-03-20 08:57:14', '69bcefcaae148742901', '7.3', 12, NULL),
(1382, 'Whistle', '<b>| 02/06/2026 (US) Horror and Mystery.</b><br>\r\nA misfit group of unwitting high school students stumble upon a cursed object, an ancient Aztec Death Whistle. They discover that blowing the whistle and the terrifying sound it emits will summon their future deaths to hunt them down.', 'Horror', 2026, '108', 'Senior', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/2d8xk8n71nea', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SSRtMn-nc63uA14schhf9Gav6tb7AxBH/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/whistle-2216.jpg', 'No', 'mOpIWXOTlY', '2026-03-20 09:02:15', '69bcf0f78e2f5920695', '6.1', 7, NULL),
(1383, 'Dangerous Animals', '<b>| 06/06/2025 (US) Horror and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nA savvy and free-spirited surfer is abducted by a shark-obsessed serial killer. Held captive on his boat, she must figure out how to escape before he carries out a ritualistic feeding to the sharks below.', 'Horror', 2025, '94', 'Mr Fire', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/ty7mklxnu36f', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UlwfYaI28kjysDbqnGi_PT-714pMMcgu/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/dangerous-animals-5434.jpg', 'No', '9ru00K4Cz6', '2026-03-23 10:56:29', '69c1003d1e524443319', '6.5', 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/dangerous-animals-backdrop-7685.jpg'),
(1384, 'Baby Girl', '<b>| 01/23/2026 (IN) Drama and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nOn a Christmas night, a guilt-ridden hospital attendant and a determined rookie cop race against time to recover a kidnapped newborn, unaware that the woman who took the baby is fighting a heartbreaking battle to finally call a child her own.', 'Indian', 2026, '144', 'Perfect', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/qxqgdss542t8', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VrE3Fdy9tiJNAL9lijsIytmgz0gA-U5q/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/baby-girl-4668.jpg', 'No', 'xh0qONquZ9', '2026-03-24 13:42:06', '69c2788e06d48592579', '5', 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/baby-girl-backdrop-3733.jpg'),
(1385, 'Bad Genius', '<b>| 05/03/2017 (TH) Drama, Crime, Thriller, and Comedy .</b><br>\r\nLynn, a brilliant student, after helping her friends to get the grades they need, develops the idea of starting a much bigger exam-cheating business.', 'Drama', 2017, '163', 'Junior Giti', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/cc2kg756pobt', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UMuO9Mf7smp92byeseB9ErfqYcNpEKS-/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/bad-genius-4321.jpg', 'No', 'DlKNFpXUiC', '2026-03-24 22:01:23', '69c2ed9320792458008', '7.9', 16, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/bad-genius-backdrop-4889.jpg'),
(1386, 'I\'m Undercover', '<b>| 02/23/2026 (CN) Action and Crime.</b><br>\r\nAn undercover officer infiltrates a pickpocket syndicate to outmaneuver its leader and dismantle the criminal network from within.', 'Action', 2026, '92', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/qaet25ofiukn', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ge7mj17dGpfyTCqor0NJtL-REyKZmIty/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/i-m-undercover-poster-8127.jpg', 'No', 'jaASNaRiK3', '2026-03-26 11:33:41', '69c4fd7552dec509316', '4', 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/i-m-undercover-backdrop-8211.jpg'),
(1387, 'Fish, Fists and Ambergris', '<b>| 11/12/2025 (VN) Action, Adventure, and Comedy.</b><br>\r\nThe treasured relic of Long DiÃªn HÆ°Æ¡ng fishing village is stolen, setting off a thrilling pursuit. Beyond its spectacular martial arts sequences, the film delivers laughter, unity, and the heartfelt human values of the coastal villagers.', 'Action', 2025, '103', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/4scafvg32nsu', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1YXCzsTPKp17S15oTv6JXRFW1kfsze4KM/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/fish-fists-and-ambergris-poster-3144.jpg', 'No', 'ohFFtRXNzB', '2026-03-26 11:38:38', '69c4fe9ed36dd593192', '6.3', 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/fish-fists-and-ambergris-backdrop-9708.jpg'),
(1388, 'Whistle', '<b>| 02/06/2026 (US) Horror and Mystery.</b><br>\r\nA misfit group of unwitting high school students stumble upon a cursed object, an ancient Aztec Death Whistle. They discover that blowing the whistle and the terrifying sound it emits will summon their future deaths to hunt them down.', 'Horror', 2026, '91', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/uftr1sc94o2l', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1J0qFRY0H3sU0i2XSZpeBu5CUrWsXOO28/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/whistle-poster-8986.jpg', 'No', 'pQNnvBimXk', '2026-03-26 11:41:31', '69c4ff4bef85c150622', '6', 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/whistle-backdrop-3494.jpg'),
(1389, 'Pretty Lethal', '<b>| 03/13/2026 (US) Action, Thriller, and Horror.</b><br>\r\nA troupe of ballerinas find themselves fighting for survival as they attempt to escape from a remote inn after their bus breaks down on the way to a dance competition.', 'Action', 2026, '88', 'Sikov', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/xlgjsc1dqokj', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IB8b2QxANTp86sXUVnrnyXFppE04dIv0/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/pretty-lethal-poster-8566.jpg', 'No', 'HTTLw9lA3d', '2026-03-27 09:54:50', '69c637ca7bd78401164', '6.7', 12, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/pretty-lethal-backdrop-3633.jpg'),
(1390, 'Pad Man', '<b>| 02/09/2018 (IN) Comedy and Drama.</b><br>\r\nUpon realizing the extent to which women are affected by their menses, a man sets out to create a sanitary pad machine and to provide inexpensive sanitary pads to the women of rural India.', 'Comedy', 2018, '160', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/eoh1yv64x03l', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qTeJW0A9z3EelfhmhpPJUrP9gVjA_ugR/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/pad-man-poster-5136.jpg', 'No', 'DfKTVPIQfL', '2026-03-28 07:59:25', '69c76e3de3836108238', '7.4', 17, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/pad-man-backdrop-8321.jpg');
