(1391, 'Pretty Lethal', '<b>| 03/13/2026 (US) Action, Thriller, and Horror.</b><br>\r\nA troupe of ballerinas find themselves fighting for survival as they attempt to escape from a remote inn after their bus breaks down on the way to a dance competition.', 'Action', 2026, '82', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/txmg2q2du101', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gPL0W0S2Iru5Ym3aw2w_Ypjf5WRJK6LY/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/pretty-lethal-poster-2581.jpg', 'No', 'D0d53xEQg4', '2026-03-28 18:58:30', '69c808b61b74b528695', '6.8', 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/pretty-lethal-backdrop-1688.jpg'),
(1392, 'Escape from the Outland', '<b>| 12/24/2025 (CN) Drama, War, and Action.</b><br>\r\nThe couple of Ma Xiao, a foreign correspondent, and Pan Wenjia, a volunteer doctor, accompanied engineer Miao Feng on a trip to the suburbs to repair a base station. During the trip, the local situation suddenly changed and the three were kidnapped by an extremist organisation. While in prison, they met Zhou Weijie, an overseas Chinese businessman. In order to find a chance of survival, they embarked on a journey of escape in the midst of barbaric warfare and chaos.', 'Drama', 2025, '131', 'Hakim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/0crppodp6ef7', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/16iaMcvZyrQCp4Txstvr5T96AGk-zafVP/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/escape-from-the-outland-poster-8242.jpg', 'No', 'yfQdyY1AAw', '2026-03-28 19:01:28', '69c80968de5d7206865', '6.5', 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/escape-from-the-outland-backdrop-9390.jpg'),
(1393, 'Agent Zeta', '<b>| 03/20/2026 (ES) Drama and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nFour Spanish ex-intelligence officers are assassinated simultaneously worldwide. The CNI discovers all participated in the covert \"Operation CiÃ©naga\" decades ago in Colombia. Zeta, the CNI\'s best operative, must hunt and protect the sole survivor, facing his deadliest global mission yet. Top Colombian agent Alfa will join Zeta, seemingly knowing more about \"CiÃ©naga\"\'s secrets than him.', 'Drama', 2026, '145', 'Mr Fire', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/pp7adykub0ap', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wPi8zrl85QIbnY_ajHbzft6dhvM7WSWK/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/agent-zeta-poster-1365.jpg', 'No', 'hWGpDKRyav', '2026-03-28 19:40:10', '69c8127a13fb1027381', '6.7', 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/agent-zeta-backdrop-4304.jpg'),
(1394, 'The Verdict', '<b>|  11/20/2025 (ID) Action, Crime, Drama, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nRaka, a court security officer, and his pregnant wife, Nina, celebrate her success in passing the bar exam. But their joyous celebration is shattered when Nina is found brutally murdered. As the trial spirals towards an unjust outcome, Raka resolves to overturn the corrupt verdict and seek justice for his late wife.', 'Action', 2025, '71', 'Mr Fire', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/f9rvjaivt9qa', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1naUPOL7kmGVWiA3syb7ZRiCp25p1Kt1J/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-verdict-poster-2742.jpg', 'No', '9vlU9NhihQ', '2026-03-28 19:43:11', '69c8132f57bf7844041', '6.7', 5, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-verdict-backdrop-6461.jpg'),
(1395, 'One Mile: Chapter One', '<b>| 02/20/2026 (US) Action and Crime.</b><br>\r\nAfter being released from prison, a father tries to reconnect with his daughter by taking her on a tour of college, but they soon find themselves fighting for more than their lost relationship when a murderous cult pursues them.', 'Action', 2026, '94', 'Dylan', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/og6wdb86ivbw', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1bZaV4D5aKm-WNx-qhtiK78Gv8i9Ec9At/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-mile-chapter-one-poster-4632.jpg', 'No', 'qxRCz0uTCq', '2026-03-29 23:23:06', '69c9983a4874b045569', '7.2', 11, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-mile-chapter-one-backdrop-9154.jpg'),
(1396, 'SAS: Red Notice', '<b>| 03/16/2021 (US) Drama, Action, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nAn off-duty SAS soldier, Tom Buckingham, must thwart a terror attack on a train running through the Channel Tunnel. As the action escalates on the train, events transpire in the corridors of power that may make the difference as to whether Buckingham and the civilian passengers make it out of the tunnel alive.', 'Action', 2021, '127', 'Sikov', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/du62u9h3nddu', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1n4OlaR4p_6ePmxKUuwB6izWvglNsViwu/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/sas-red-notice-poster-4666.jpg', 'No', 'r7NiIhWHtb', '2026-03-31 21:27:09', '69cc200dbd427154357', '5.8', 16, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/sas-red-notice-backdrop-4486.jpg'),
(1397, 'Bad Voodoo', '<b>| 02/10/2026 (US) Horror.</b><br>\r\nTwo escaped convicts break into a house and take a hostage, only to discover that the hideout houses something far more dangerous: a voodoo curse born from a grieving coupleâ€™s thirst for vengeance. As the night spirals into terror, they must battle an unseen power that feeds on guilt, blood, and lost souls.', 'Horror', 2026, '109', 'Kim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/3su6w3fpq1s9', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ySfezLrAGrgcX2oIOxgRCUkVR72EaVFP/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/bad-voodoo-poster-7890.jpg', 'No', 'ORTc1F58yl', '2026-04-02 16:30:49', '69ce7d99a9d49336434', '3.3', 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/bad-voodoo-backdrop-3698.jpg'),
(1398, 'Skinwalker Island', '<b>| 12/08/2025 (US) Horror.</b><br>\r\nAfter their grandmother\'s death, Lucy and Miles return to their family\'s swamp island, only to face buried secrets, eerie visions, and their volatile cousin Chet. As myths come alive, the trio is pulled into a nightmare of shape-shifting terror and reckoning.', 'Horror', 2025, '89', 'Kim', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/cwcw7hgw4pxt', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1J8wzM2jp3sQFwsNEm6locWiVwd0XqSYo/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/skinwalker-island-poster-7606.jpg', 'No', 'QUNw9byaqP', '2026-04-02 16:35:54', '69ce7eca0881c225864', '5', 2, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/skinwalker-island-backdrop-2696.jpg'),
(1399, 'In a Violent Nature', '<b>| 05/31/2024 (CA) Drama, Horror, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nThe enigmatic resurrection, rampage, and retribution of an undead monster in a remote wilderness unleashes an iconic new killer after a locket is removed from a collapsed fire tower that entombed its rotting corpse.', 'Horror', 2024, '83', 'Senior', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/4cv3u00jwy29', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k7evljkn8528Eluqn2BYdZjnn8-PuhFu/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/in-a-violent-nature-poster-2799.jpg', 'No', 'K9S6pPpE9j', '2026-04-02 16:44:02', '69ce80b275b5d166917', '5.6', 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/in-a-violent-nature-backdrop-5615.jpg'),
(1400, 'The Strangers: Chapter 1', '<b>| 05/17/2024 (US) Horror and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nAfter their car breaks down in an eerie small town, a young couple are forced to spend the night in a remote cabin. Panic ensues as they are terrorized by three masked strangers who strike with no mercy and seemingly no motives.', 'Horror', 2024, '89', 'Dylan', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/z1ycmmmh1sag', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cOoWOD7oBGxU55GV-MlTd41zN_RYfpoO/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-strangers-chapter-1-poster-9597.jpg', 'No', 'CUoIc82wwp', '2026-04-02 16:49:45', '69ce8209069ec493209', '5.6', 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-strangers-chapter-1-backdrop-9331.jpg'),
(1401, 'Troll 2', '<b>| 12/01/2025 (RW) Action, Fantasy, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nWhen a dangerous new troll unleashes devastation across their homeland, Nora, Andreas and Major Kris embark on their most perilous mission yet.', 'Sci-Fi', 2025, '108', 'Gaheza', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/g953oqhsxcug', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1A11yuaNpqJkL5m4CvW2Djzsw3RvKtfi2/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/troll-2-poster-7741.jpg', 'No', 'Rt3pjTSCVG', '2026-04-03 09:52:51', '69cf71d3de2b5651179', '6.4', 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/troll-2-backdrop-9314.jpg'),
(1402, 'The Strangers: Chapter 2', '<b>| 09/26/2025 (US) Horror and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nAfter learning that one of their victims, Maya, is still alive, The Strangers return to finish the job. With nowhere to run and no one to trust, Maya soon finds herself in a brutal fight for survival against psychopaths more than willing to kill anyone who stands in their way.', 'Horror', 2025, '92', 'B The Great', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/und61i0p796v', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-L3wb-VTQpBQmuGrUPEPoDwv8iHbVQA7/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-strangers-chapter-2-poster-2589.jpg', 'No', 'RC4yZTJZwQ', '2026-04-08 20:58:44', '69d6a5640518e983920', '6.4', 2, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-strangers-chapter-2-backdrop-9808.jpg'),
(1403, 'Along with the Gods: The Last 49 Days A', '<b>| 08/01/2018 (KR) Action, Adventure, Fantasy, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nAs the deceased soul Ja-hong and his three afterlife guardians prepare for their remaining trials for reincarnation, the guardians soon come face to face with the truth of their tragic time on Earth 1,000 years earlier.', 'Action', 2018, '59', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/sviydl0g2bhr', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OIT63eUJm1aCc-2rNYOFgMswAVxC-JKV/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/along-with-the-gods-the-last-49-days-a-poster-6322.jpg', 'No', 'NKZFnaQKZj', '2026-04-08 21:22:25', '69d6aaf1bcbb3789419', '8.1', 5, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/along-with-the-gods-the-last-49-days-a-backdrop-4393.jpg'),
(1404, 'Mom', '<b>|  07/07/2017 (IN) Crime, Drama, and Thriller.</b><br>\r\nAfter her stepdaughter is sexually assaulted at a party, a furious mother sets out to destroy the lives of the four perpetrators who walked free.', 'Indian', 2017, '138', 'Rocky', 'https://bysetayico.com/e/m8o5udyuf78v', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1JbYwsmDUTIfCqkTqz80DjZDZHLHCqGoA/view?usp=drive_link', 'https://media.theonemovies.com/mom-poster-4222.jpg', 'No', 'a1AbHrvwRj', '2026-04-09 09:10:16', '69d750d8550a0292257', '7.5', 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/mom-backdrop-1752.jpg');
