(2015, 'Night has Come', 'Trapped in the deadly cursed \"Mafla Game,\" the students of Yoo-il High must play the game to survive, while unraveling the mysteries behindÂ theÂ curse.', 'Drama', 2023, 'Rocky', 1, 12, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/night-has-come-7218.jpg', '2025-08-20 15:48:10', '68a5d21a11', '7.8', 7, NULL),
