(2030, 'House of David S1', 'Tells the story of the ascent of the biblical figure, David, who becomes the most celebrated king of Israel. The series follows the once-mighty King Saul as he falls victim to his own pride. At the direction of God, the prophet Samuel anoints an unlikely, outcast teenager as the new king.', 'Drama', 2025, 'Savimbi', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/house-of-david-s1-3768.jpg', '2025-11-12 08:17:20', '69142670811ca019569', '8', 9, NULL),
