(2058, 'Money Heist: Korea - Joint Economic Area ', 'Disguised under the shadows of a mask, a crew of desperados band together under the leadership of a criminal mastermind known only as â€œThe Professorâ€ to pull off the biggest heist Korea has ever seen.', 'Action', 2022, 'Rocky', 1, 6, '1767767315.webp', '2026-01-07 08:28:34', '695dfd127c2b5455208', '7.7', 27, NULL),
