(2060, 'Hwarang: The Poet Warrior Youth ', 'An elite group of young warriors trained in morals and martial arts finds love and friendship in Silla during Koreaâ€™s ancient Three Kingdoms period.', 'Drama', 2016, 'Rocky', 1, 20, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/hwarang-the-poet-warrior-youth-8736.jpg', '2026-02-04 09:23:49', '6968961cca594038679', '7.9', 37, NULL),
(2061, 'Shadow Love', 'General Li Shuang of Taijin finds a man who has lost his memory and names him Jin\'an. Jin\'an devotes himself to accompanying Li Shuang; however, as he gradually regains his memories, he discovers that he is actually a prince from an enemy nation. Once bound by love, the two are forced into battle. Together, they confront challenges that test their loyalties and beliefs, striving to resolve the conflict and uphold the justice they both believe in.', 'Drama', 2025, 'B The Great', 1, 38, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/shadow-love-7628.jpg', '2026-01-19 23:16:43', '696e9f3b59452714316', '8.5', 19, NULL),
(2062, 'Conflict', 'A small, Finnish seaside town is preparing to celebrate midsummer\'s eve. An unknown enemy arrives and takes the entire area hostage.', 'Action', 2024, 'Mr Fire', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/conflict-8614.jpg', '2026-01-24 17:08:13', '6974e05ddc229209095', '6.4', 12, NULL),
(2063, 'HIS & HERS', 'Two estranged spouses â€” one a detective, the other a news reporter â€” vie to solve a murder in which each believes the other is a prime suspect.', 'Drama', 2026, 'Sikov', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/his-hers-2322.jpg', '2026-01-25 18:44:43', '6976487b0a912721924', '7.1', 23, NULL),
(2064, 'Stranger Things S1', 'When a young boy vanishes, a small town uncovers a mystery involving secret experiments, terrifying supernatural forces, and one strange little girl.', 'Horror', 2016, 'Dylan', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/stranger-things-7474.jpg', '2026-01-25 19:43:16', '69765634311c8637271', '8.6', 19, NULL),
(2065, 'Steal', 'A typical day at Lochmill Capital is upended when armed thieves burst in and force Zara and her best friend Luke to execute their demands. In the aftermath, conflicted detective Rhys races against time to find out who stole Â£4 billion pounds of people\'s pensions and why.', 'Drama', 2026, 'Sikov', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/steal-4015.jpg', '2026-01-26 08:00:13', '697702edf40de272230', '8.2', 40, NULL),
(2066, 'Billionaires\' Bunker', 'When a group of billionaires takes shelter in a luxury bunker, an old feud between two families resurfaces amid an unprecedented global conflict.', 'Drama', 2025, 'Rocky', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/billionaires-bunker-5409.jpg', '2026-03-20 08:50:34', '697899446c72c696625', '6.5', 74, NULL),
(2067, 'Criminal Code', 'To crack the code of an investigation into a larger-than-life robbery, federal agents need to get creative.', 'Action', 2023, 'Mr Fire', 1, 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/criminal-code-1389.jpg', '2026-02-02 19:42:27', '697dff09dc00e977605', '7.5', 8, NULL),
(2068, 'Stranger Things S2', 'Season 2 of Stranger Things premiered on October 27, 2017.\r\n\r\nIt\'s been nearly a year since Will\'s strange disappearance. But life\'s hardly back to normal in Hawkins. Not even close.\r\n', 'Horror', 2017, 'Dylan', 2, 9, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/stranger-things-s2-7299.jpg', '2026-03-02 22:52:08', '697f8ea7c5a3b492545', '8.2', 14, NULL),
(2069, 'Billionaires\' Bunker', 'When a group of billionaires takes shelter in a luxury bunker, an old feud between two families resurfaces amid an unprecedented global conflict.', 'Drama', 2025, 'Sikov', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/billionaires-bunker-1437.jpg', '2026-02-01 21:15:13', '697fa64181fe1616583', '6.5', 14, NULL),
(2070, 'Homeland S3', '\r\nSeason 3 of Homeland premiered on September 28, 2013.\r\n\r\nCarrie goes to extraordinary lengths to solve the latest crisis at the CIA while dealing with a deeply personal secret. Brody struggles to survive. Saul must walk a tightrope and play many opposing sides to keep his job at the CIA and try to revive his troubled marriage. Quinn has a crisis of faith.\r\n', 'Drama', 2013, 'Rocky', 3, 12, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/homeland-s3-9518.jpg', '2026-02-02 22:02:01', '698102b9b24f3879096', '7.5', 9, NULL),
(2071, 'Always a Witch', 'A young 17th-century witch time travels to the future to save the man she loves, but first must adjust to present-day Cartagena and defeat a dark rival.', 'Drama', 2019, 'Rocky', 1, 10, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/always-a-witch-3333.jpg', '2026-02-09 09:58:09', '6984efdc582b7032279', '7', 23, NULL),
(2072, 'Commander Karan Saxena', 'As ISI-aided terror looms over the nation, RAW agent Karan Saxena must race against the clock to avert the attacks. But conspirators lurk in every shadow!', 'Action', 2024, 'Hakim', 1, 20, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/commander-karan-saxena-8975.jpg', '2026-02-07 09:42:00', '6986ecc8a30cc634315', '5', 6, NULL),
(2073, 'Our Universe', '<b>|  Comedy and Drama.</b><br>\r\nTwo in-laws forced to raise their orphaned nephew together slowly overcome their misunderstandings, finding personal growth and an unexpected romance through co-parenting under one roof.', 'Comedy', 2026, 'Saga Mwiza', 1, 24, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/our-universe-9357.jpg', '2026-03-19 17:50:02', '698e3a958b1de660155', '9.5', 28, NULL),
(2074, 'All of Us Are Dead', '<b>|  Action & Adventure, Drama, and Sci-Fi & Fantasy.</b><br>\r\nA high school becomes ground zero for a zombie virus outbreak. Trapped students must fight their way out â€” or turn into one of the rabid infected.', 'Action', 2022, 'Sankara', 1, 12, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/all-of-us-are-dead-8851.jpg', '2026-02-14 09:08:14', '69901f5ee0313071880', '7.3', 11, NULL),
(2075, 'The Pendragon Cycle: Rise of the Merlin', '<b>|  Sci-Fi & Fantasy, Action & Adventure, Family, and Drama.</b><br>\r\nMerlin, the immortal son of the bard Taliesin and Atlantean Princess Charis, is followed through his tragic upbringing, descent into madness, and shocking disappearance, leading to the legend that surrounds him. Set before King Arthur\'s birth, Merlin, assumed dead or a myth, reemerges in sub-Roman Britain to unite the fractured kingdoms under threat from Saxon invaders.', 'Sci-Fi', 2026, 'Hakim', 1, 7, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-pendragon-cycle-rise-of-the-merlin-4660.jpg', '2026-03-10 19:51:52', '6990237a5f9e6862024', '8.4', 15, NULL),
(2076, 'Lioness S2', '<b>|  Drama and War & Politics.</b><br>\r\nSeason 2 of Lioness premiered on October 27, 2024. <br>\r\nIn Season 2, as the CIA\'s fight against terror moves closer to home, Joe, Kaitlyn, and Byron enlist a new Lioness operative to infiltrate a previously unknown threat. With pressure mounting from all sides, Joe is forced to confront the profound personal sacrifices she has made as the leader of the Lioness program.', 'Action', 2024, 'Sikov', 2, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/lioness-s2-9917.jpg', '2026-02-18 08:51:38', '6995617a6ee6d000974', '8.2', 19, NULL),
(2077, 'The Night Agent S1', '<b>|  Action & Adventure, Drama, and Mystery.</b><br>\r\nBrought together by a midnight phone call, an FBI agent and a cybersecurity expert must unravel an ever-growing web of political conspiracies.', 'Action', 2023, 'Junior Giti', 1, 12, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-night-agent-3192.jpg', '2026-02-18 09:18:30', '699567c67a3b7112888', '7.7', 12, NULL),
(2078, 'The Night Agent S2', '<b>|  Action & Adventure, Drama, and Mystery.</b><br>\r\nSeason 2 of The Night Agent premiered on January 23, 2025.<br>\r\nThe hunt for a CIA agent accused of leaking secrets puts Peter and Rose in the crosshairs of a ruthless intelligence broker and a deadly war criminal.\r\n', 'Action', 2025, 'Junior Giti', 2, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-night-agent-s2-2713.jpg', '2026-02-21 08:12:52', '69994ce44ff73075799', '7', 6, NULL),
(2079, 'Bank Under Siege', '<b>|  Crime, Drama, and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nSeason 1 of Bank Under Siege premiered on November 8, 2024.<br>\r\nSpain, 1981: When armed men hold up a bank and take hundreds hostage, a reporter races against the authorities to uncover the true motive for the heist.', 'Crime', 2024, 'Junior Giti', 1, 5, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/bank-under-siege-3422.jpg', '2026-02-21 08:23:39', '69994f6bf0e51477099', '6.7', 7, NULL),
(2080, 'Tunnel', '<b>|  05/25/2017 - Crime and Mystery.</b><br>\r\nA police detective from 1986 travels in time to the present to save his daughter.', 'Crime', 2017, 'Rocky', 1, 16, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/tunnel-5038.jpg', '2026-03-03 22:30:32', '699958de89f0a158001', '8', 25, NULL),
(2081, 'Spartacus: House of Ashur', '<b>| 12/05/2025 -  Drama and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nIn a world where he survived the events of Spartacus, Ashur clawed his way to power, owning the same ludus that once owned him. Allying with a fierce gladiatrix, Ashur ignites a new kind of spectacle that offends the elite.', 'Drama', 2025, 'Hakim', 1, 10, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/spartacus-house-of-ashur-1112.jpg', '2026-02-22 05:10:02', '699a738a0e7cc483414', '6.8', 8, NULL),
(2082, 'Unfamiliar', '<b>|  Action & Adventure, Drama, and Crime.</b><br>\r\nWhen the past catches up with two former spies, their biggest challenge isn\'t car chases, shootouts or fistfights â€” it\'s telling each other the truth.', 'Action', 2026, 'Sikov', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/unfamiliar-8570.jpg', '2026-02-24 15:53:03', '699dad3f03eba092554', '7.5', 23, NULL),
(2083, 'The Night Manager', '<b>|  Drama, Mystery, and Crime.</b><br>\r\nFormer British soldier Jonathan Pine navigates the shadowy recesses of Whitehall and Washington where an unholy alliance operates between the intelligence community and the secret arms trade. To infiltrate the inner circle of lethal arms dealer Richard Onslow Roper, Pine must himself become a criminal.', 'Drama', 2016, 'Six', 1, 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-night-manager-2892.jpg', '2026-02-24 23:35:17', '699e199587b7b635709', '7.7', 6, NULL),
(2084, 'Last Samurai Standing', '<b>|  Action & Adventure and Drama.</b><br>\r\nIn the early Meiji era, Shujiro, once known as an undefeated samurai, decides to participate in a deadly survival game to save his family and villagers.', 'Action', 2025, 'B The Great', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/last-samurai-standing-1073.jpg', '2026-03-31 09:21:06', '699ed8d34dc55190534', '7.8', 15, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/last-samurai-standing-backdrop-3616.jpg'),
(2085, 'The Continental: From the World of John Wick', '<b>|  Crime, Drama, and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nThe origin behind the iconic hotel-for-assassins through the eyes and actions of a young Winston Scott, as he\'s dragged into the Hell-scape of 1970\'s New York City to face a past he thought he\'d left behind. Winston charts a deadly course through the hotel\'s mysterious underworld in a harrowing attempt to seize the hotel where he will eventually take his future throne.', 'Action', 2023, 'Gaheza', 1, 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-continental-from-the-world-of-john-wick-7225.jpg', '2026-02-26 22:26:24', '69a0ac700b27a179086', '7.4', 4, NULL),
(2086, 'Traveler', '<b>| Drama and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nJay, Tyler and Will are friends who have spent the last two years in grad school. A simple prank to rollerblade through one of New York City\'s most famous museums makes Jay and Tyler prime suspects in a terrorist bombing. They\'re unable to turn to authorities when they realize they can\'t prove Will even exists. In every photo from the past two years, he has managed to block his face. Who will believe them?', 'Drama', 2007, 'Sankara', 1, 5, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/traveler-3159.jpg', '2026-02-28 22:10:06', '69a34b9e62736088876', '6.7', 3, NULL),
(2087, 'Fate: The Winx Saga', '<b>| Sci-Fi & Fantasy and Drama.</b><br>\r\nThe coming-of-age journey of five fairies attending Alfea, a magical boarding school in the Otherworld where they must learn to master their powers while navigating love, rivalries, and the monsters that threaten their very existence.', 'Sci-Fi', 2021, 'Cyber', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/fate-the-winx-saga-2431.jpg', '2026-02-28 22:26:55', '69a34f8fbf5a9769770', '8', 4, NULL),
(2088, 'The Longest Night', '<b>| Crime.</b><br>\r\nArmed forces surround a psychiatric prison in order to abduct an incarcerated serial killer â€” but aren\'t prepared for the battle that ensues.', 'Crime', 2022, 'Dylan', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-longest-night-8520.jpg', '2026-02-28 22:38:49', '69a35259d1a80328857', '6.8', 6, NULL),
(2089, 'Blood Coast', '<b>| Action & Adventure, Crime, and Drama.</b><br>\r\nAs a vicious drug dealer tries to overtake Marseille, a rogue police captain and his daredevil team welcome a new recruit with an agenda of her own.', 'Action', 2023, 'Sikov', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/blood-coast-7903.jpg', '2026-03-01 22:41:37', '69a4a481958e5542757', '7.4', 6, NULL),
(2090, 'Wolf Pack', '<b>| Sci-Fi & Fantasy and Drama.</b><br>\r\nWhen a raging wildfire releases a supernatural creature, four young adults find themselves drawn together under a full moon.', 'Sci-Fi', 2023, 'Sankara', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/wolf-pack-6027.jpg', '2026-03-02 22:43:18', '69a5f66604300987181', '7.8', 7, NULL),
(2091, 'Switch', '<b>| Drama, Mystery, and Comedy.</b><br>\r\nA man is a swindler. He is smart enough to take the bar exam, but he could not become a prosecutor. Disregarding favoritism and biases by prosecutors, the man makes criminals pay for crimes that prosecutors did not.', 'Drama', 2018, 'Rocky', 1, 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/switch-1123.jpg', '2026-03-04 08:02:44', '69a7cb041aee2812410', '6.8', 20, NULL),
(2092, 'Tehran S1', '<b>| Drama.</b><br>\r\nTamar is a Mossad hacker-agent who infiltrates Tehran under a false identity to help destroy Iran\'s nuclear reactor. But when her mission fails, Tamar must plan an operation that will place everyone dear to her in jeopardy.', 'Drama', 2020, 'Sankara', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/tehran-1464.jpg', '2026-03-04 08:09:46', '69a7ccaa028ac370956', '7.5', 12, NULL),
(2093, 'Tehran S2', '<b>| 07/05/2022 - Drama.</b><br>\r\nTamar is a Mossad hacker-agent who infiltrates Tehran under a false identity to help destroy Iran\'s nuclear reactor. But when her mission fails, Tamar must plan an operation that will place everyone dear to her in jeopardy.', 'Drama', 2022, 'Sankara', 2, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/tehran-s2-4603.jpg', '2026-03-04 08:19:16', '69a7cee44429e288208', '7.8', 14, NULL),
(2094, 'Stranger Things S3', '<b>| 04/07/2019 - Sci-Fi & Fantasy, Mystery, and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nBudding romance. A brand-new mall. And rabid rats running toward danger. It\'s the summer of 1985 in Hawkins ... and one summer can change everything.', 'Horror', 2019, 'Dylan', 3, 2, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/stranger-things-s3-7328.jpg', '2026-03-05 19:31:05', '69a9bdd9352c1385676', '8.2', 11, NULL),
(2096, 'A Knight of the Seven Kingdoms', '<b>| Drama, Sci-Fi & Fantasy, and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nA century before the events of Game of Thrones, two unlikely heroes wandered Westeros: a young, naive but courageous knight, Ser Duncan the Tall, and his diminutive squire, Egg. Set in an age when the Targaryen line still holds the Iron Throne and the last dragon has not yet passed from living memory, great destinies, powerful foes, and dangerous exploits await these improbable and incomparable friends.', 'Drama', 2026, 'Perfect', 1, 6, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/a-knight-of-the-seven-kingdoms-2840.jpg', '2026-03-16 10:45:24', '69b7c3245e133883909', '8.5', 8, NULL),
(2097, 'The Manipulated', '<b>| Crime and Drama.</b><br>\r\nTaejoong\'s life is torn apart when he\'s framed for a heinous crime and imprisoned. Discovering it was all orchestrated by someone on the outside, he embarks on a rage-fueled quest for revenge.', 'Crime', 2025, 'Junior Giti', 1, 12, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/the-manipulated-7411.jpg', '2026-03-20 09:36:29', '69bcf8fd92c4c330822', '8.3', 25, NULL),
(2098, 'ONE PIECE', '<b>| Action & Adventure and Sci-Fi & Fantasy.</b><br>\r\nWith his straw hat and ragtag crew, young pirate Monkey D. Luffy goes on an epic voyage for treasure.', 'Action', 2023, 'Gaheza', 1, 8, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-piece-7833.jpg', '2026-03-21 20:16:06', '69bee0663f3f5931603', '7.7', 14, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-piece-backdrop-6021.jpg'),
(2099, 'ONE PIECE S2: Into the Grand Line', '<b>| Action & Adventure and Sci-Fi & Fantasy.</b><br>\r\nIn ONE PIECE: Into the Grand Line, Luffy and the Straw Hats set sail for the extraordinary Grand Line - a legendary stretch of sea where danger and wonder await at every turn. As they journey through this unpredictable realm in search of the world\'s greatest treasure, they\'ll encounter bizarre islands and a host of formidable new enemies.', 'Action', 2026, 'Perfect', 2, 7, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-piece-s2-into-the-grand-line-9924.jpg', '2026-03-24 13:30:12', '69c275c401402302338', '6.8', 20, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-piece-s2-into-the-grand-line-backdrop-1321.jpg'),
(2100, 'ONE PIECE S2: Into the Grand Line', '<b>| Action & Adventure and Sci-Fi & Fantasy.</b><br>\r\nIn ONE PIECE: Into the Grand Line, Luffy and the Straw Hats set sail for the extraordinary Grand Line - a legendary stretch of sea where danger and wonder await at every turn. As they journey through this unpredictable realm in search of the world\'s greatest treasure, they\'ll encounter bizarre islands and a host of formidable new enemies.', 'Action', 2026, 'Gaheza', 2, 4, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-piece-s2-into-the-grand-line-5595.jpg', '2026-03-27 08:43:10', '69c2eebb78fce699881', '6.8', 30, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/one-piece-s2-into-the-grand-line-backdrop-1913.jpg'),
(2101, 'Cashero', '<b>| Action & Adventure and Drama.</b><br>\r\nAn ordinary man who inherits super strength discovers a greater evil out to steal his power. The one catch? Every use drains money from his wallet.', 'Action', 2025, 'Junior Giti', 1, 2, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/cashero-poster-6038.jpg', '2026-03-28 07:54:23', '69c76d0fb349d213989', '7.3', 35, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/cashero-backdrop-1846.jpg'),
(2102, 'Last Samurai Standing', '<b>| Action & Adventure and Drama.</b><br>\r\nIn the early Meiji era, Shujiro, once known as an undefeated samurai, decides to participate in a deadly survival game to save his family and villagers.', 'Action', 2025, 'Sankara', 1, 2, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/last-samurai-standing-poster-7493.jpg', '2026-04-01 13:39:12', '69cd03e0850bc908347', '7.8', 15, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/last-samurai-standing-backdrop-5806.jpg'),
(2103, 'Taken', '<b>| Action & Adventure, Crime, Drama, and Comedy.</b><br>\r\nThe origin story of younger, hungrier, former Green Beret Bryan Mills as he deals with a personal tragedy that shakes his world. As he fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge, Mills is pulled into a career as a deadly CIA operative, a job that awakens his very particular, and very dangerous, set of skills.', 'Action', 2017, 'Rocky', 1, 7, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/taken-poster-3991.jpg', '2026-04-08 21:02:08', '69d0b394734db534669', '6.5', 19, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/taken-backdrop-2269.jpg'),
(2104, 'Young Sherlock', '<b>| Action & Adventure and Mystery.</b><br>\r\nSherlock Holmes is a disgraced young man, raw and unfiltered, when he finds himself wrapped up in a murder case that threatens his liberty. His first ever case unravels a globe-trotting conspiracy that changes his life forever.', 'Action', 2026, 'Perfect', 1, 7, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/young-sherlock-poster-5062.jpg', '2026-04-04 14:11:36', '69d0fff8b0b66092850', '8', 7, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/young-sherlock-backdrop-9482.jpg'),
(2105, 'La Brea', '<b>| Sci-Fi & Fantasy, Drama, and Action & Adventure.</b><br>\r\nAn epic adventure begins when a massive sinkhole opens in the middle of Los Angeles, pulling hundreds of people and buildings into its depths. Those who fell in find themselves in a mysterious and dangerous primeval land, where they have no choice but to band together to survive. Meanwhile, the rest of the world desperately seeks to understand what happened. In the search for answers, one family torn apart by this disaster will have to unlock the secrets of this inexplicable event to find a way back to each other.', 'Sci-Fi', 2021, 'Sankara', 1, 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/la-brea-poster-9322.jpg', '2026-04-08 11:49:04', '69d62490a4673711192', '7.4', 3, 'https://media.theonemovies.com/la-brea-backdrop-5291.jpg');
